<p>
<b>IRC chat on <uri link="http://www.freenode.org/">Freenode</uri>:</b>.
</p>

<p>
The gentoo developers and helpers run the following channels for
mutual benefit, it is purely voluntary, and open to everyone. Feel
free to pop in and say Hello! Please keep the language clean in
#gentoo and #gentoo-dev. Read the policy (if applicable) and the topic.
Owners of other Gentoo channels are permitted to set their own policies and
please be aware of the ban procedures in place in
<uri link="irc-gentoo-policy.xml">#gentoo</uri>.
Additionally, please do not bring bots into Gentoo channels without first
consulting channel operators.
This includes bot-like scripts such as "seen" scripts. Do not run <c>ctcp
version</c> or alike against the channel or users without their prior knowledge.
</p>

